title: Increase in cake staking rewards manual and auto
body: Dear Chefs , fix the APR 100% , its the signature of pancakeswap , this syrup pools are crazy and beautiful , why do we have reduce the passive income from our own beautiful cake token staking for other pools and farms , please increase the rewards for cake syrup pools auto and manual and fix them while the others can be adjusted on time to time , our pancakeswap hotbox must be absolutely untouchable with the highest rewards so one will be able to  compete the rewards in the whole universe.best Wishes , we are one. long live chefs.
